@DOC.text:
Written a long time ago in a land far away.  This is a single player
version of yahtzee.  Written when I was learning rexx so it isn't
as 'good' of code as I'd probably write now but... hey it works
and who has time to rewrite a working set of code.
I have tried to make it as near to the standard yahtzee rules
as possible.  Edit member YZ to your received dataset names
and place YZ in a sysproc/sysexec concatenated dataset.
please email me with any info or problems you
may encounter.
   Thanks and ENJOY
Paul Lemons AKA taltyman (Talty is a small city near Dallas, TX)
taltyman@excite.com email

YZ.text:
/* REXX */
'ISPEXEC LIBDEF ISPPLIB'
'ISPEXEC LIBDEF ISPPLIB DATASET ID('''XXXX.YAH.PANELS''')'
'ALTLIB  ACT    APP(CLIST)     DSN('''XXXX.YAH.CLIST''')'
ZEE
'ISPEXEC LIBDEF ISPPLIB'
'ALTLIB  DEA    APP(CLIST)'
RETURN

ZEE.text:
/* REXX */
TRACE ERR
DO CNTD=1 TO 5 BY 1
  D.CNTD = RANDOM(1,6)
END
D1 = D.1
D2 = D.2
D3 = D.3
D4 = D.4
D5 = D.5

U2 = ''
U3 = ''
U4 = ''
U5 = ''
U6 = ''
LC = ''
L3 = ''
L4 = ''
LF = ''
LS = ''
LL = ''
LY = ''
MS = ''
RS = 'NO'
R1 = 'R'
R2 = 'R'
R3 = 'R'
R4 = 'R'
R5 = 'R'
TR = 1
SC = '0'
LB = '0'
LT = '0'
UT = '0'
GT = '0'
UB = '0'
US = '0'
TRACE OFF
"ISPEXEC VGET (HS1 HS2 HS3 HS4 HS5) PROFILE"
IF HS1 = '' THEN HS1 = 0
IF HS2 = '' THEN HS2 = 0
IF HS3 = '' THEN HS3 = 0
IF HS4 = '' THEN HS4 = 0
IF HS5 = '' THEN HS5 = 0
TRACE ERR
"ISPEXEC VPUT (HS1 HS2 HS3 HS4 HS5 RS) PROFILE"
"ISPEXEC VPUT (D1 D2 D3 D4 D5 R1 R2 R3 R4 R5 TR) PROFILE"
"ISPEXEC VPUT (UT GT LT US U1 U2 U3 U4 U5 U6 LB UB) PROFILE"
"ISPEXEC VPUT (MS L3 L4 LF LC LS LL LY LY LS LT) PROFILE"
"ISPEXEC SELECT PANEL(ZEE)"
RETURN

ZEELB.text:
/* REXX */
TRACE ERR
LB = 0
LT = 0
"ISPEXEC VGET (D1 D2 D3 D4 D5 LB LT) PROFILE"
IF D1 = D2 THEN
IF D2 = D3 THEN
IF D3 = D4 THEN
IF D4 = D5 THEN DO
   LB = LB + 100
  IF LB > 300 THEN RETURN
  IF LB > 0 THEN DO
    LT = LT + 100
    MS = 'CONGRATULATIONS'
    "ISPEXEC VPUT (LB LT MS) PROFILE"
  END
END
RETURN

ZEER.text:
/* REXX */
TRACE ERR
RS = 'NO'
"ISPEXEC VGET (RS) PROFILE"
IF RS = 'YES' THEN DO
  TR = 0
  D1 = ''
  D2 = ''
  D3 = ''
  D4 = ''
  D5 = ''
  R1 = 'R'
  R2 = 'R'
  R3 = 'R'
  R4 = 'R'
  R5 = 'R'
  RS = 'NO'
  END
ELSE DO
  TR = 1
  D1 = RANDOM(1,6)
  D2 = RANDOM(1,6)
  D3 = RANDOM(1,6)
  D4 = RANDOM(1,6)
  D5 = RANDOM(1,6)
  R1 = 'R'
  R2 = 'R'
  R3 = 'R'
  R4 = 'R'
  R5 = 'R'
END
"ISPEXEC VPUT (TR D1 D2 D3 D4 D5 R1 R2 R3 R4 R5 RS) PROFILE"
RETURN

ZEET.text:
/* REXX */
TRACE ERR
CALL ZEEUB
"ISPEXEC VGET (UT LT U1 U2 U3 U4 U5 U6) PROFILE"
"ISPEXEC VGET (L3 L4 LF LS LL LY LC LB) PROFILE"
SELECT
WHEN U1 = '' THEN  NOP
WHEN U2 = '' THEN  NOP
WHEN U3 = '' THEN  NOP
WHEN U4 = '' THEN  NOP
WHEN U5 = '' THEN  NOP
WHEN U6 = '' THEN  NOP
WHEN L3 = '' THEN  NOP
WHEN L4 = '' THEN  NOP
WHEN LF = '' THEN  NOP
WHEN LS = '' THEN  NOP
WHEN LL = '' THEN  NOP
WHEN LY = '' THEN  NOP
WHEN LC = '' THEN  NOP
OTHERWISE
  DO
    "ISPEXEC VGET (HS1 HS2 HS3 HS4 HS5) PROFILE"
    GT = LT + UT
    IF GT >= HS1 THEN DO
      HS5 = HS4
      HS4 = HS3
      HS3 = HS2
      HS2 = HS1
      HS1 = GT
    END
    IF GT < HS1 THEN IF GT >= HS2 THEN DO
      HS5 = HS4
      HS4 = HS3
      HS3 = HS2
      HS2 = GT
    END
    IF GT < HS2 THEN IF GT >= HS3 THEN DO
      HS5 = HS4
      HS4 = HS3
      HS3 = GT
    END
    IF GT < HS3 THEN IF GT >= HS4 THEN DO
      HS5 = HS4
      HS4 = GT
    END
    IF GT < HS4 THEN IF GT > HS5 THEN DO
      HS5 = GT
    END
    RS = 'YES'
    "ISPEXEC VPUT (HS1 HS2 HS3 HS4 HS5 RS) PROFILE"
    MS = 'Thanks for playing. Enter "99" to start a new game!'
    IF LT + UT > 300 THEN MS = 'GREAT GAME!' MS
    "ISPEXEC VPUT (MS) PROFILE"
  END
END
GT = LT + UT
"ISPEXEC VPUT (GT) PROFILE"
RETURN

ZEEUB.text:
/* REXX */

ZEEYC.text:
/* REXX */
TRACE ERR
"ISPEXEC VGET (D1 D2 D3 D4 D5 LY) PROFILE"
IF LY = 50 THEN RETURN
IF LY = 0 THEN RETURN
IF D1 = D2 THEN
IF D2 = D3 THEN
IF D3 = D4 THEN
IF D4 = D5 THEN DO
  MS = 'YOU HAVE YAHTZEE.  TAKE THE 50 POINTS INSTEAD'
  "ISPEXEC VPUT (MS) PROFILE"
  RETURN 4
END
RETURN
